{
  "stem": "7506.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, in Holland, those old houses have very high stairs-- very steep and very narrow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it's not easy to quickly go down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's much easier for me at that age, then, than what it may have been for my parents or indeed, much older people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Very dangerous to go fast down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they made us get out and stand outside, all-- all-- all in groups of people outside the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was in-- in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It wasn't cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they made us march to a station, which I've never been to before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because it was a completely, shall I say, not unknown area of Amsterdam, but not an area where I had frequented before.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I didn't really know if there was a station, or where I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went to-- to the station, which is called the [DUTCH], which is still there today-- the station.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were standing on the platforms for a long time, I think until daybreak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we were all put in-- in-- in cattle wagons at the station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My mother and father, and my sister and I, and other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But no one else that I knew at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were cramped in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the train went on its way, but we didn't know to where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't know where-- to where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My parents may have known-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Other people may have known.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't remember how long the train journey was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It may have been the rest of that day, which was that-- in the morning, we got into the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It may have taken the rest of that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't know whether it took an overnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
